## Three-Layer Architecture

```
Component
  ↓  uses hooks from
state/*/api.ts  (RTK Query — caching, invalidation, state sync)
  ↓  calls functions from
api/*.ts        (pure SDK wrappers — no state, no cache, just network)
  ↓  calls
TradlySDK       (Tradly JS SDK)
```

**Rule:** Components never import from `api/`. Components never import from `state/*/slice.ts` except for action dispatchers (`logout`). All data flows through RTK Query hooks.

