## Adding a New Domain (e.g. Orders)

Follow this checklist to add a new feature domain to the boilerplate:

1. **`api/orders.ts`** — wrap SDK calls, use the correct payload builder from `api/sdk-context.ts`
2. **`types/order.types.ts`** — define input/response types
3. **`state/orders/api.ts`** — create RTK Query `createApi` with `LocalState` interface, `queryFn` pattern
4. **`state/orders/selectors.ts`** — `useQueryState` helpers for deep components
5. **`state/store.ts`** — add `[ordersApi.reducerPath]: ordersApi.reducer` to `combineReducers` and `.concat(ordersApi.middleware)`
6. **`flows/orders-flows.mdc`** — copy structure from `cart-flows.mdc`, document invalidation

