## SDK Payload Builder Reference

All four builders live in `api/sdk-context.ts`. Pick the right one — wrong builder = SDK error.

| Builder | Use when | SDK call shape |
|---|---|---|
| `buildSdkPayload` | `TradlySDK.user.*` (auth only) | `{ data: {...}, pkKey, currency, language }` |
| `buildAppQueryPayload` | `getListings`, `getCarts` | `{ bodyParam: {...}, pkKey, authKey, currency, language }` |
| `buildAppMutationPayload` | `addToCart`, `deleteFromCart`, `clearCart` | `{ data: {...}, pkKey, authKey, currency, language }` |
| `buildAppDirectPayload` | `likeListing`, `unlikeListing`, `getListingDetail` | `{ ...params, pkKey, authKey, currency, language }` |

